### ─────────────────────────────
### DISHES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear plato (ADMIN)
### Requiere menu_type_id: obtenerlo desde GET /menu-types
POST {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Tarta de verdura",
  "description": "Tarta de verdura con queso y huevo",
  "menu_type_id": "a6d7a71d-5da6-4515-8272-f98b0dc18f2f"
}

###

### Listar todos los platos
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar platos por tipo de menú
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes?menu_type_id=55179510-1f80-4ad4-900f-e11c7fefbb05
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener plato por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/dishes/one?dishId={{dishId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar plato (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/dishes/{{dishId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Milanesa con puré de zapallo",
  "description": "Milanesa de carne con puré de zapallo",
  "active": true
}

###

### Eliminar plato (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/dishes/{{dishId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
